headline: American Airlines, MasterCard announce extension of partnership
summary: American Airlines (AAL) and Mastercard (MA) announced an extension of their decades-long partnership. The agreement secures Mastercard as the exclusive payment network partner for American’s co-branded credit cards. Together, American and Mastercard will continue to enhance the AAdvantage program.
